  "keyFeatures": [
    "Sphere, box, line, and triangle collision primitives with surface/piece type metadata",
    "CColModel and CCollisionData for managing collections of collision volumes",
    "CCollision static class with extensive test and process methods (sphere-sphere, sphere-box, line-triangle, etc.)",
    "CPhysical base class providing physics simulation: mass, velocity, friction, elasticity, collision response",
    "CColStore for streaming collision data files in and out of memory using a quad-tree spatial index",
    "CColAccel caching system for fast collision loading and IPL entity acceleration",
    "Compressed float and vector types for memory-efficient storage of normals and triangle planes",
    "CTempColModels providing pre-allocated shared collision models for peds, vehicles, and props",
    "Camera collision subsystem with sphere-cast and cone-cast utilities",
    "Multi-platform support including WDMOBILE-specific collision model sections"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
    "CCollision::TestSphereSphere / ProcessSphereSphere",
